verbose_text: Taken together, these data demonstrated that miR-125a-5p inhibition exacerbated hyperglycemia and hyperlipidemia, enhanced hepatic lipogenesis and gluconeogenesis, and suppressed glycogen synthesis through up-regulation of STAT3.
